<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 01:21:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加密货币黑客事件导致顶级 DeFi 贷款机构流出 90 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-20/crypto-hack-sparks-9-billion-outflows-from-biggest-defi-lender</link><description>周末的一次黑客攻击导致一个鲜为人知的加密项目流失了近 3 亿美元，引发了去中心化金融投资者的信任危机，用户从 DeFi 最大的借贷平台上撤走了数十亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJi9cHiPGeM4/v1/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 10:05:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-20/crypto-hack-sparks-9-billion-outflows-from-biggest-defi-lender</guid></item><item><title>Strategy 购买了 25.4 亿美元的比特币，为 2024 年底以来的最大一笔</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-20/strategy-buys-2-54-billion-of-bitcoin-most-since-november-2024</link><description>Michael Saylor&amp;#39;s Strategy Inc. 在过去 7 天内购买了 25.4 亿美元的比特币，这是这家数字资产财务公司自 2024 年 11 月以来对原始加密货币的最大一笔收购。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iGVXQX8gUByg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 12:39:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-20/strategy-buys-2-54-billion-of-bitcoin-most-since-november-2024</guid></item><item><title>前高盛量化董事总经理从加密货币投资公司加入 DRW</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-20/ex-goldman-quant-md-joins-drw-from-crypto-investment-firm-xbto</link><description>前高盛集团董事总经理 Javier Rodriguez-Alarcon 已从加密货币投资公司 XBTO 加盟自营交易巨头 DRW Holdings LLC。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iM_5LW7EMaTY/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 10:27:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-20/ex-goldman-quant-md-joins-drw-from-crypto-investment-firm-xbto</guid></item></channel></rss>